{"sectionId":723,"sectionIdLiteral":"723","humanId":"lesson-303","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"The holy Christ is born in me today.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 303"},"annotation":"W-303","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-303\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"723#1\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Watch with me, angels, watch with me today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Let all God‚Äôs holy Thoughts surround me, and be still with me while Heaven‚Äôs Son is born.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>Let earthly sounds be quiet, and the sights to which I am accustomed disappear.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Let Christ be welcomed where He is at home.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>And let Him hear the sounds He understands, and see but sights that show His Father‚Äôs Love.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Let Him no longer be a stranger here, for He is born again in me today.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"723#2\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Your Son is welcome, Father.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>He has come to save me from the evil self I made.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>He is the Self that You have given me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>He is but what I really am in truth.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>He is the Son You love above all things.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>He is my Self as You created me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:7\"><span class=\"snr\">7</span>It is not Christ that can be crucified.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"723#2:8\"><span class=\"snr\">8</span>Safe in Your Arms let me receive Your Son.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Watch with me, angels, watch with me today. Let all God‚Äôs holy Thoughts surround me, and be still with me while Heaven‚Äôs Son is born. Let earthly sounds be quiet, and the sights to which I am","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 303: The holy Christ is born in me today | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†303 ‚ÄúThe holy Christ is born in me today‚Äù: Watch with me, angels, watch with me today. Let all God‚Äôs holy Thoughts‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"9. What Is the Second Coming?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":720,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-second-coming"]}},{"label":"Lesson 303","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":723,"slugs":["lesson-303","the-holy-christ-is-born-in-me-today"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"9. What Is the Second Coming?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":720,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-second-coming"]}},{"label":"Lesson 303","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":723,"slugs":["lesson-303","the-holy-christ-is-born-in-me-today"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,